{"tid":2369261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"用戶暴增超負荷 Signal大故障","createTime":"2021-01-17T03:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T04:25:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"82140fd8a82144d65530c891869315e60e373a5e","tid":2369261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/DEN6RM3QLFBMDNSZNVTVEYTGVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FDEN6RM3QLFBMDNSZNVTVEYTGVI%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=ccf72c3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FDEN6RM3QLFBMDNSZNVTVEYTGVI%2F&h=58a39e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/DEN6RM3QLFBMDNSZNVTVEYTGVI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n用戶暴增超負荷 Signal大故障<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自WhatsApp單方面更新私隱條款惹來用戶不滿「轉會」後，免費加密通訊軟件Signal用戶數量暴增，惟已超出本身網絡基建負載力，就算已加緊加裝伺服器仍追不上需求，導致前晚開始出現大規模技術故障，使不少用戶無法收發訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正加快新增伺服器<br />\n<br />\nSignal近日在多國成為最多人下載的通訊軟件，程式上周二在Google Play的下載量一日內由1,000萬暴升至5,000萬。但全球各地用戶前晚開始發現出問題，Signal亦承認正處理技術問題，在Twitter多次推文表示希望可盡快恢復服務，又指「我們在恢復服務方面已取得進展。私隱是我們最優先考慮的事，現在增加負載力僅次於此」。<br />\n<br />\nSignal營運總監哈德（Aruna Harder）表示：「我們本周每天都以前所未有的速度加快新增伺服器，擴充容量以應付高流量，但今天超出我們最樂觀估計。數以百萬計的新用戶正表達對私隱的重視。請耐心等候。」<br />\n<br />\n據監察故障網站Downdetector接獲故障報告數字，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nSignal總部位於矽谷，由WhatsApp共同創。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CDn7hJiiTUNJSelox51HXHBVyys=/2168x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CHYXNU4G3ZFBVORSYYDXX2MFTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCDn7hJiiTUNJSelox51HXHBVyys%3D%2F2168x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCHYXNU4G3ZFBVORSYYDXX2MFTI.jpg&h=065485f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■故障期間，Signal版面出現一條置頂提示，解釋程式正出現技術故障。互聯網"},{"pid":"7f457cdb180854e64bcf85074f2c297880c3557e","tid":2369261,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e53929adeda322580982551b9561457ac193f4d","tid":2369261,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2a2c49bc1af48f71ab12b78b1b0ee19cc1b0ee","tid":2369261,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"話轉icq tg line 嗰班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b41167e0629d7d84aecd3fbfef834c918ee1e6","tid":2369261,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432e2c1543d498b5ed70dacddb420a3e18028477","tid":2369261,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"用得番了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9bb6a86aa48979e332394bc0de8834c1716a17","tid":2369261,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f2a2c49bc1af48f71ab12b78b1b0ee19cc1b0ee","tid":2369261,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"話轉icq tg line 嗰班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"無問題，只要唔好轉返whatsapp咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32854b256ab91f66479f51afea34ca1d476a0b","tid":2369261,"uid":28